description:
&lt;p&gt;The North of England Commissioning Support Unit (NECS) works across the UK to support health and social care customers in meeting their strategic and operational challenges, improving outcomes and increasing efficiency.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our current customers include local authorities, Clinical Commissioning Groups (CCGs), a range of healthcare providers including those that make up emerging Integrated Care Services (ICS), third and private sector organisations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An opportunity has arisen for a motivated, enthusiastic and flexible PA to join the Corporate Admin Team. The team provides a comprehensive, effective and efficient administrative service to the Executive Team within the organisation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;The post is based within the Corporate Administrative Team at John Snow House, Durham. However,a flexible approach is needed to meet service delivery needs and there is a requirement to travel between NECS bases and other venues. Additionally the postholder will provide day to day supervision for Band 3 administrators.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Experience of taking minutes at complex/committee internal and external meetings is essential and the postholder must demonstrate a flexible approach and be able to travel independently when required. &lt;span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;The Corporate Admin Team delivers an administrative service between the hours of 8.30am- 5.30pm Monday to Thursday and 8.30am- 5.00pm on Friday. This is a full-time post working 37.5 hours per week covering service delivery hours on a rota basis. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;NECS offers:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;A competitive salary&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Access to the NHS Pensions Scheme&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Annual leave of between 27 and 33 days plus Bank Holidays&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Easily accessible offices near bus stops&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Free parking&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Please note, this advert may close earlier than advertised if sufficient applications are received, therefore you are encouraged to apply as soon as possible if you are interested in this role. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
